(4, 1, '2013-07-24 20:15:15', '2013-07-24 20:15:15', '<div id="childrens" class="group">\r\n<h1>Děti k adopci</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n„Adoptovat“ děti, znamená financovat jejich vzdělání a podílet se na celkovém zlepšení jejich životní situace. Na podpoře jednoho dítěte se mohou podílet kolektivy, rodiny nebo skupiny přátel.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Andrew Okiria</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait1.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Asheri Ankunda</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait2.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Benjamin Friday</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait3.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Boaz Twinomujumi</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait4.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Boniface Nahabwe</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Andrew Okiria</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait1.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Asheri Ankunda</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=48"><img src="http://bwindiorphans.org/wp-content/themes/quora/images/portrait2.jpg" alt="" /></div><span>Benjamin Friday</span></a></div>\r\n<div class="children"><div class="bubble"><a href="?page_id=4